{"id":1324,"date":"2024-08-04T19:50:42","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T19:50:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1324"},"modified":"2024-08-04T19:50:42","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T19:50:42","slug":"mission-011","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-011\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #011: Average Angler"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #011: Average Angler<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Polder Town, North House near Croagunk &#8211; Fisherman inside<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Polder Town<\/li>\n<li>Must have already spoken to the Fisherman in Gurun Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Hook 10 Pokemon while Fishing<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>10 Dive Balls<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A Fisherman has received some corporate sponsorship and wants to give you some prizes every time you reach a fishing milestone. For hooking 10 Pok\u00e9mon with a fishing rod, he\u2019ll give you 10 Dive Balls.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>This mission starts in Polder Town, but it has a requirement: you must have spoken to the Fisherman in Gurun Town first. <\/p>\n<p>He\u2019s in the house northeast of the Regi monument in Gurun Town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-fishermans-1st-location.jpg\" alt=\"The Fisherman\u2019s first location \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fisherman\u2019s first location<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-fisherman-tests-you-1st.jpg\" alt=\"The Fisherman tests you first \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fisherman tests you first<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>He\u2019ll ask you if you\u2019ve hooked a Pok\u00e9mon with a fishing rod at least 3 times. <\/p>\n<p>If you have, he will leave for a house in Polder Town and give you a <strong>Pearl<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-fishermans-house-in-polder-town.jpg\" alt=\"The Fisherman\u2019s house in Polder Town \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fisherman\u2019s house in Polder Town<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The same Fisherman will then be in Polder Town, next to the Poke Mart and the Croagunk show.<\/p>\n<p>The Fisherman has received a fishing rod sponsorship from Cube Corp., and as part of that, he wants you to hook as many Pok\u00e9mon as you can. His first task for you is to hook 10 of them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-fishermans-1st-task.jpg\" alt=\"The Fisherman\u2019s first task \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fisherman\u2019s first task<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/05-pokemon-unbound-fishing-in-cootes-bog.jpg\" alt=\"Fishing in Cootes Bog \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Fishing in Cootes Bog<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>To complete the mission, you need to have hooked 10 Pok\u00e9mon with a fishing rod. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cHooked\u201d means attracted into battle &#8211; you don\u2019t have to capture or even defeat them, you can escape from battle and it will still count.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/011\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-reward-from-the-fisherman.jpg\" alt=\"The first reward from the Fisherman \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first reward from the Fisherman<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After you\u2019ve hooked ten, go back to the Fisherman and he\u2019ll give you 10 Dive Balls. <\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> This mission starts a series of fishing missions &#8211; the next one is <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-026\/\">Mission #026: Great Piscator<\/a>.\n<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1325,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1324","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1324","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"w